query:
SELECT
                bike.id,
                bike.model_id,
                bike.name,
                bike.thumbnail,
                bike.description,
                bike.view_count,
                bike.like_count,
                bike.created_at,
                bike.edited_at,
                bike.hidden,
                
                brand.id as brand_id,
                brand.name as brand_name,
                model.name as model_name                
            FROM
                "Bike" AS bike
                    INNER JOIN
                "Model" AS model ON model.id = bike.model_id
                    INNER JOIN
                "Brand" AS brand ON brand.id = model.brand_id
            WHERE
                bike.id = $1
